Coinciding with several Bicentennial Independence celebrations in Latin
America, from June to October 2010 German and Latin American [bloggers
[es]](http://superdemokraticos.com/es/autoren/) will be writing for _Los
Superdemokraticos_ [about](http://superdemokraticos.com/es/category/english/)
their “daily lifes [sic] in international political contexts.” Posts are
published in [German](http://superdemokraticos.com/) and
[Spanish](http://superdemokraticos.com/es); five texts are translated into
[English](http://superdemokraticos.com/es/category/english/) each month.

